channel.title: WTF? How does this even happen?
channel.description: Well I began adding tutorial island to my server but when I clicked on the RuneScape Guide, it displayed the dialogue of the NPC with the Id of 1 which was a man. How does this even happen. The Id of the RuneScape guide is 945, I made a case in the dialogue.java file called "case 945 :" and put all the correct dialogue, however clicking on it displays the dialogue of a man with the id of 1
